LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ControllingArea
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT KOKRS, WAERS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tka01" WHERE KOKRS IS NOT NULL and (WAERS is NULL or ucase(WAERS) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null )) and MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_CompanyCode
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT t001.BUKRS, t001.WAERS, tka02.KOKRS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001" as t001 inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tka02" as tka02 on t001.mandt = tka02.mandt and t001.bukrs = tka02.bukrs and tka02.gsber = '''' WHERE t001.BUKRS IS NOT NULL and tka02.bukrs is not null AND tka02.KOKRS IS NOT NULL and (t001.WAERS is NULL or ucase(t001.WAERS) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) ) and t001.mandt = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Plant
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT t001w.WERKS, t001k.BUKRS, t001w.STRAS,t001w.PSTLZ, t001w.ORT01, t001w.LAND1, t001w.REGIO FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" as t001w inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001k" as t001k on t001w.mandt= t001k.mandt and t001w.BWKEY = t001k.BWKEY WHERE t001w.WERKS IS NOT NULL AND t001k.BUKRS IS NOT NULL and t001w.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_OverheadGroup
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT tck14.KOSGR, t001w.WERKS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tck14" AS tck14 INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" AS t001w ON tck14.BWKEY = t001w.BWKEY AND tck14.MANDT = t001w.MANDT WHERE tck14.KOSGR IS NOT NULL AND t001w.WERKS IS NOT NULL AND tck14.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_UoM
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: select distinct (CASE WHEN uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID is not null then uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID else MSEHI END) as MSEHI, dim.DESTINATION_DIMENSION_ID as DIMID, ZAEHL, NENNR, EXP10, ADDKO from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t006" as t006 inner join "sap.plc.db::map.t_dimension_mapping" as dim on t006.DIMID = dim.SOURCE_DIMENSION_ID left outer join "sap.plc.db::map.t_uom_mapping" as uom on t006.MSEHI = uom.SOURCE_UOM_ID where IFNULL(t006.MSEHI, '''') <> '''' and t006.MSEHI not in (''10'',''STD'') and t006.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_CostCenter
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(CSKS.KOSTL)=0 then CSKS.KOSTL else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM CSKS.KOSTL )END) AS KOSTL, CSKS.KOKRS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_csks" as CSKS WHERE CSKS.KOSTL IS NOT NULL and CSKS.KOKRS is not NULL and CSKS.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_csks" AS CSKS1 WHERE CSKS1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CSKS1.KOKRS = CSKS.KOKRS AND CSKS1.KOSTL = CSKS.KOSTL) AND CSKS.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) AND CSKS.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Account
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(CSKB.KSTAR)=0 then CSKB.KSTAR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM CSKB.KSTAR )END) AS KSTAR, CSKB.KOKRS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cskb" as CSKB WHERE CSKB.KSTAR IS NOT NULL and CSKB.KOKRS is not NULL and CSKB.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cskb" AS CSKB1 WHERE CSKB1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CSKB1.KSTAR= CSKB.KSTAR AND CSKB1.KOKRS = CSKB.KOKRS) AND CSKB.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and CSKB.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Process
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT CBPR.PRZNR, CBPR.KOKRS, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(CBPR.VKSTA)=0 then CBPR.VKSTA else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM CBPR.VKSTA )END) AS VKSTA, null as COMMENT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cbpr" AS CBPR WHERE CBPR.PRZNR IS NOT NULL and CBPR.KOKRS is not NULL and CBPR.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cbpr" AS CBPR1 WHERE CBPR1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CBPR1.PRZNR = CBPR.PRZNR AND CBPR1.KOKRS = CBPR.KOKRS) AND CBPR.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and CBPR.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ValuationClass
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT BKLAS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t025" WHERE BKLAS IS NOT NULL and MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ProfitCenter
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(CEPC.PRCTR)=0 then CEPC.PRCTR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM CEPC.PRCTR )END) AS PRCTR, CEPC.KOKRS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cepc" as CEPC WHERE CEPC.PRCTR IS NOT NULL and CEPC.KOKRS is not NULL and CEPC.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cepc" AS CEPC1 WHERE CEPC1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CEPC1.PRCTR = CEPC.PRCTR AND CEPC1.KOKRS = CEPC.KOKRS) AND CEPC.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and CEPC.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_BusinessArea
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT GSBER FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tgsb" WHERE GSBER IS NOT NULL and MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialType
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT MTART FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t134" WHERE MTART IS NOT NULL and MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialGroup
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT MATKL FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t023"  WHERE MATKL IS NOT NULL AND MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Material
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT DISTINCT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(MATNR)=0 then MATNR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM MATNR )END) AS MATNR, IFNULL( uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID, MEINS ) AS MEINS, mara.MATKL, mara.MTART, CASE WHEN mara.CADKZ = '''' OR mara.CADKZ IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS CADKZ, 0 AS IS_PHANTOM_MATERIAL, CASE WHEN mara.KZKFG = '''' OR mara.KZKFG IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS KZKFG FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_mara" AS mara LEFT OUTER JOIN "sap.plc.db::map.t_uom_mapping" AS uom ON mara.MEINS = uom.SOURCE_UOM_ID WHERE ifnull(mara.LVORM,'''')<>''X'' AND IFNULL(mara.MATNR, '''') <> '''' AND (IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID, MEINS) IN (SELECT DISTINCT UOM_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_uom")) AND mara.mandt = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_DocumentType
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT tdwa.DOKAR FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tdwa" as tdwa WHERE tdwa.DOKAR IS NOT NULL AND tdwa.MANDT=''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Status
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT tdws.DOKAR, tdws.DOKST FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tdws" as tdws WHERE tdws.DOKAR IS NOT NULL AND tdws.DOKST IS NOT NULL AND tdws.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Document
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT draw.DOKAR, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(DOKNR)=0 then DOKNR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM DOKNR )END) AS DOKNR, draw.DOKVR, draw.DOKTL, draw.DOKST, draw.LABOR, CASE WHEN draw.CADKZ = '''' OR draw.CADKZ IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS CADKZ FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_draw" as draw WHERE ifnull(draw.LOEDK,'''')<>''X'' AND draw.DOKAR IS NOT NULL AND draw.DOKNR IS NOT NULL AND draw.DOKVR IS NOT NULL AND draw.DOKTL IS NOT NULL AND draw.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_DocumentMaterial
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: select distinct drad.DOKAR, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(drad.DOKNR)=0 then drad.DOKNR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM drad.DOKNR )END) AS DOKNR, drad.DOKVR, drad.DOKTL, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(drad.OBJKY)=0 then drad.OBJKY else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM drad.OBJKY )END) AS OBJKY from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_drad" as drad where ifnull(drad.DELFLAG,'''')<>''X'' and drad.DOKOB = ''MARA'' and drad.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Vendor
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT LIFNR,LAND1,CASE WHEN NAME1 IS NOT NULL AND NAME2 IS NOT NULL THEN NAME1 || '' '' || NAME2 WHEN NAME1 IS NOT NULL AND NAME2 IS NULL THEN NAME1 WHEN NAME1 IS NULL AND NAME2 IS NOT NULL THEN NAME2 ELSE '''' END AS NAME1, ORT01,PSTL2,REGIO,STRAS,LOEVM,CASE WHEN STKZN = '''' OR STKZN IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS STKZN FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_lfa1" WHERE IFNULL(LOEVM,'''') <> ''X'' AND IFNULL(CVP_XBLCK ,'''') <> ''X'' AND LIFNR IS NOT NULL AND MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_Customer
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT KUNNR,LAND1,CASE WHEN NAME1 IS NOT NULL AND NAME2 IS NOT NULL THEN NAME1 || '' '' || NAME2 WHEN NAME1 IS NOT NULL AND NAME2 IS NULL THEN NAME1 WHEN NAME1 IS NULL AND NAME2 IS NOT NULL THEN NAME2 ELSE '''' END AS NAME1,ORT01,PSTLZ,REGIO,STRAS,CASE WHEN STKZN = '''' OR STKZN IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS STKZN FROM  "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_kna1"  WHERE ifnull(LOEVM,'''')<>''X'' AND ifnull(CVP_XBLCK,'''')<>''X'' AND KUNNR IS NOT NULL AND MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_CurrencyConversion
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: select distinct ''STANDARD'' as EXCHANGE_RATE_TYPE_ID, tcurr.FCURR, tcurr.TCURR, tcurf.FFACT, tcurf.TFACT, tcurr.UKURS, TO_DATE(99999999 - tcurr.GDATU) as VALID_FROM from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tcurr" as tcurr inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tcurf" as tcurf on tcurr.MANDT = tcurf.MANDT and tcurr.KURST = tcurf.KURST and tcurr.FCURR = tcurf.FCURR and tcurr.TCURR = tcurf.TCURR where ucase(tcurr.FCURR) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) and ucase(tcurr.TCURR) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) and (select max(TO_DATE(99999999 - tcurff.GDATU)) from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tcurf" as tcurff where tcurff.MANDT = tcurr.MANDT and tcurff.KURST = tcurr.KURST and tcurff.FCURR = tcurr.FCURR and tcurff.TCURR = tcurr.TCURR group by tcurff.MANDT, tcurff.KURST, tcurff.FCURR, tcurff.TCURR ) <=  TO_DATE(99999999 - tcurr.GDATU) and tcurr.MANDT = ''800'' and tcurr.UKURS > 0 union select distinct ''STANDARD'' as EXCHANGE_RATE_TYPE_ID, tcurr.FCURR, tcurr.TCURR, tcurf.TFACT as FFACT, tcurf.FFACT as TFACT, 1 / ( (-1 ) * tcurr.UKURS ) as UKURS, TO_DATE(99999999 - tcurr.GDATU) as VALID_FROM from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tcurr" as tcurr inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tcurf" as tcurf on tcurr.MANDT = tcurf.MANDT and tcurr.KURST = tcurf.KURST and tcurr.FCURR = tcurf.TCURR and tcurr.TCURR = tcurf.FCURR where ucase(tcurr.FCURR) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) and ucase(tcurr.TCURR) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) and (select max(TO_DATE(99999999 - tcurff.GDATU)) from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tcurf" as tcurff where tcurff.MANDT = tcurr.MANDT and tcurff.KURST = tcurr.KURST and tcurff.FCURR = tcurr.TCURR and tcurff.TCURR = tcurr.FCURR group by tcurff.MANDT, tcurff.KURST, tcurff.FCURR, tcurff.TCURR ) <=  TO_DATE(99999999 - tcurr.GDATU) and tcurr.MANDT = ''800'' and tcurr.UKURS < 0

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialPlant
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT DISTINCT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(marc.MATNR)=0 then marc.MATNR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM marc.MATNR )END) AS MATNR, IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID,mara.MEINS) AS MEINS, marc.WERKS, marc.LOSGR, mbew.BKLAS, mbew.KOSGR FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_marc" AS marc inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" AS t001w on marc.mandt = t001w.mandt and marc.WERKS=t001w.WERKS inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_mbew" AS mbew on marc.mandt = mbew.mandt and marc.matnr = mbew.matnr and t001w.bwkey= mbew.bwkey and mbew.bwtar = '''' inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_mara" AS mara on marc.mandt = mara.mandt and marc.matnr = mara.matnr LEFT OUTER JOIN "sap.plc.db::map.t_uom_mapping" AS uom ON mara.MEINS = uom.SOURCE_UOM_ID WHERE ifnull(marc.LVORM,'''')<>''X'' AND IFNULL(marc.MATNR, '''') <> '''' AND (IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID, mara.MEINS) IN (SELECT DISTINCT UOM_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_uom")) and marc.mandt = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialPrice
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: select distinct price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(mbew.MATNR)=0 then mbew.MATNR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM mbew.MATNR )END) AS MATNR, (case when t001w.werks is null or t001w.werks =''''  then ''*'' else t001w.werks end) as WERKS,''*'' as VENDOR_ID,''*'' as PROJECT_ID,''*'' as CUSTOMER_ID,(case WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_STANDARD_PRICE'' THEN TO_DATE(CONCAT(ifnull(mbew.LFGJA,''2000''),ifnull(mbew.LFMON,''01''))) WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_MOVING_PRICE'' THEN TO_DATE(CONCAT(ifnull(mbew.LFGJA,''2000''),ifnull(mbew.LFMON,''01''))) WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE1'' THEN mbew.ZPLD1 WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE2'' THEN mbew.ZPLD2 WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE3'' THEN mbew.ZPLD3 end) as VALID_FROM, null as VALID_TO, 1 as VALID_FROM_QUANTITY , null as VALID_TO_QUANTITY , marc.EKGRP as EKGRP, null as PURCHASING_DOCUMENT , null as LOCAL_CONTENT , 0 as PRICE_FIXED_PORTION , (case WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_STANDARD_PRICE'' THEN mbew.STPRS WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_MOVING_PRICE'' THEN mbew.VERPR WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE1'' THEN mbew.ZPLP1 WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE2'' THEN mbew.ZPLP2 WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE3'' THEN mbew.ZPLP3 end) as PRICE_VARIABLE_PORTION, t001.WAERS as WAERS, MBEW.PEINH as PEINH, IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID, mara.MEINS) as MEINS from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_mbew" as mbew left outer join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_mara" as mara on mbew.MATNR = mara.MATNR and mbew.MANDT = mara.MANDT left outer join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001k" as t001k on mbew.BWKEY = t001k.BWKEY and mbew.MANDT = t001k.MANDT left outer join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001" as t001 on t001.BUKRS = t001k.BUKRS and t001.MANDT = t001k.MANDT left outer join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" as t001w on t001w.BWKEY = t001k.BWKEY and t001w.MANDT = t001k.MANDT left outer join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_marc" as marc on mbew.MATNR = marc.MATNR and t001w.WERKS = marc.WERKS and mbew.MANDT = marc.MANDT left outer join "sap.plc.db::map.t_uom_mapping" AS uom ON mara.MEINS = uom.SOURCE_UOM_ID inner join ( select ''ERP_STANDARD_PRICE'' as PRICE_SOURCE_ID from dummy union all select ''ERP_MOVING_PRICE'' as PRICE_SOURCE_ID from dummy union all select ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE1'' as PRICE_SOURCE_ID from dummy union all select ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE2'' as PRICE_SOURCE_ID from dummy union all select ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE3'' as PRICE_SOURCE_ID from dummy ) as price_sources on 1 = 1 where mbew.BWTAR = '''' and ifnull(mbew.LVORM,'''')<>''X'' and (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_STANDARD_PRICE'' THEN mbew.STPRS ELSE 1 END) is not null and (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_STANDARD_PRICE'' THEN mbew.STPRS ELSE 1 END) <> 0.99 and  (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_MOVING_PRICE'' THEN mbew.VERPR ELSE 1 END) is not null and (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_MOVING_PRICE'' THEN mbew.VERPR ELSE 1 END) <> 0.99 and  (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE1'' THEN mbew.ZPLP1 ELSE 1 END) <> 0.99 and (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE2'' THEN mbew.ZPLP2 ELSE 1 END) is not null and (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE2'' THEN mbew.ZPLP2 ELSE 1 END) <> 0.99 and  (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE3'' THEN mbew.ZPLP3 ELSE 1 END) is not null and (CASE WHEN price_sources.PRICE_SOURCE_ID = ''ERP_PLANNED_PRICE3'' THEN mbew.ZPLP3 ELSE 1 END) <> 0.99 and (IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID, mara.MEINS) IN (SELECT DISTINCT UOM_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_uom")) and (t001.WAERS is NULL or ucase(t001.WAERS) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) ) and mbew.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialAccountDetermination
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT DISTINCT tka02.KOKRS, ''*'' as MTART, t001w.WERKS, CASE WHEN IFNULL(t030.BKLAS,'''') = '''' OR t030.BKLAS = '' '' THEN ''*'' ELSE t030.BKLAS END AS BKLAS, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(t030.KONTS)=0 then t030.KONTS else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM t030.KONTS )END) AS KONTS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t030" AS t030 inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001k" as t001k on t001k.MANDT = t030.MANDT and t001k.BWMOD = t030.BWMOD inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" as t001w on t001w.MANDT = t001k.MANDT and t001w.BWKEY = t001k.BWKEY inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tka02" as tka02 on t001w.mandt = tka02.mandt and t001k.BUKRS = tka02.BUKRS and tka02.gsber = '''' inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001" as t001 on tka02.mandt = t001.mandt  and tka02.bukrs = t001.bukrs  and t030.KTOPL = t001.KTOPL WHERE t030.KOMOK = ''VBR'' and t030.KTOSL = ''GBB'' and t030.mandt = ''800'' AND IFNULL(t030.BWMOD,'''')<>'''' UNION SELECT DISTINCT tka02.KOKRS, ''*'' as MTART, ''*'' as WERKS, CASE WHEN IFNULL(t030.BKLAS,'''') = '''' OR t030.BKLAS = '' '' THEN ''*'' ELSE t030.BKLAS END AS BKLAS, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(t030.KONTS)=0 then t030.KONTS else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM t030.KONTS )END) AS KONTS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t030" AS t030 inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001" as t001 on t030.mandt = t001.mandt and t030.KTOPL = t001.KTOPL inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tka02" as tka02 on t001.mandt = tka02.mandt and t001.BUKRS = tka02.BUKRS and tka02.gsber = '''' WHERE t030.KOMOK = ''VBR'' and t030.KTOSL = ''GBB'' and t030.mandt = ''800'' and IFNULL(t030.BWMOD,'''')=''''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ActivityType
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT CSLA.LSTAR, CSLA.KOKRS, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(CSLA.VKSTA)=0 then CSLA.VKSTA else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM CSLA.VKSTA )END) AS VKSTA FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_csla" AS CSLA WHERE CSLA.LSTAR IS NOT NULL and CSLA.KOKRS is not NULL and CSLA.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_csla" AS CSLA1 WHERE CSLA1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CSLA1.LSTAR = CSLA.LSTAR AND CSLA1.KOKRS = CSLA.KOKRS) AND CSLA.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and CSLA.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ControllingAreaText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT KOKRS, lang.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, BEZEI FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tka01" JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" AS lang ON lang.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and lang._valid_from <= current_timestamp and lang._valid_to is null WHERE KOKRS IS NOT NULL and (WAERS is NULL or ucase(WAERS) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null )) and MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_CompanyCodeText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT BUKRS, lang.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, BUTXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001" JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" AS lang ON lang.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 WHERE BUKRS in ( SELECT distinct t001.BUKRS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001" as t001 inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tka02" as tka02 on t001.mandt= tka02.mandt and t001.bukrs = tka02.bukrs and tka02.gsber = '''' WHERE t001.BUKRS IS NOT NULL and tka02.bukrs is not null AND tka02.KOKRS IS NOT NULL and (t001.WAERS is NULL or ucase(t001.WAERS) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) ) and t001.mandt = ''800'' ) and MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_PlantText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT texttable.WERKS,lang.LANGUAGE AS LANGU,texttable.NAME1 FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" as texttable inner join (SELECT t001w.WERKS FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" as t001w inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001k" as t001k on t001w.mandt= t001k.mandt and t001w.BWKEY = t001k.BWKEY WHERE t001w.WERKS IS NOT NULL AND t001k.BUKRS IS NOT NULL) as maintable ON texttable.WERKS = maintable.WERKS JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" AS lang ON lang.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 where texttable.mandt = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_OverheadGroupText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTableOverheadGroup.KOSGR, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, t001w.WERKS, textTableOverheadGroup.TXZSCHL FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tck15" AS textTableOverheadGroup INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t001w" AS t001w ON textTableOverheadGroup.BWKEY = t001w.BWKEY AND textTableOverheadGroup.MANDT = t001w.MANDT INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTableOverheadGroup.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTableOverheadGroup.KOSGR IS NOT NULL AND t001w.WERKS IS NOT NULL AND textTableOverheadGroup.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_UoMText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT mainTable.MSEHI, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.MSEH3, textTable.MSEHT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t006a" as textTable inner join (select distinct (CASE WHEN uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID is not null then uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID else MSEHI END) as MSEHI, t006.MSEHI as MSEHI_NO_CONVERT from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t006" as t006 inner join "sap.plc.db::map.t_dimension_mapping" as dim on t006.DIMID = dim.SOURCE_DIMENSION_ID left outer join "sap.plc.db::map.t_uom_mapping" as uom on t006.MSEHI = uom.SOURCE_UOM_ID where IFNULL(t006.MSEHI, '''') <> '''' and t006.MSEHI not in (''10'',''STD'') and t006.MANDT = ''800'' ) as mainTable on textTable.MSEHI = mainTable.MSEHI_NO_CONVERT INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null where textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_CostCenterText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(textTable.KOSTL)=0 then textTable.KOSTL else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM textTable.KOSTL )END) AS KOSTL,textTable.KOKRS,languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU,textTable.KTEXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cskt" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.KOSTL IS NOT NULL and textTable.KOKRS IS NOT NULL and textTable.DATBI = ( SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cskt" AS CSKT1 WHERE CSKT1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CSKT1.KOKRS = textTable.KOKRS AND CSKT1.KOSTL = textTable.KOSTL AND CSKT1.SPRAS = textTable.SPRAS) AND textTable.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_AccountText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(cskuTextTable.KSTAR)=0 then cskuTextTable.KSTAR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM cskuTextTable.KSTAR )END) AS KSTAR, tka01.KOKRS, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, cskuTextTable.KTEXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_csku" as cskuTextTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tka01" as tka01 on cskuTextTable.mandt = tka01.mandt and cskuTextTable.ktopl = tka01.ktopl INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on cskuTextTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE cskuTextTable.KSTAR IS NOT NULL and tka01.KOKRS IS NOT NULL and cskuTextTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ActivityTypeText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.LSTAR, textTable.KOKRS, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.KTEXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cslt" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.LSTAR IS NOT NULL and textTable.KOKRS IS NOT NULL and textTable.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cslt" AS CSLT1 WHERE CSLT1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CSLT1.LSTAR = textTable.LSTAR AND CSLT1.KOKRS = textTable.KOKRS AND CSLT1.SPRAS = textTable.SPRAS) AND textTable.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ProcessText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.PRZNR, textTable.KOKRS, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.KTEXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cbpt" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.PRZNR IS NOT NULL and textTable.KOKRS IS NOT NULL and textTable.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cbpt" AS CBPT1 WHERE CBPT1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CBPT1.PRZNR= textTable.PRZNR AND CBPT1.KOKRS = textTable.KOKRS AND CBPT1.SPRAS = textTable.SPRAS) AND textTable.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ValuationClassText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.BKLAS, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.BKBEZ FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t025t" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.BKLAS IS NOT NULL and textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ProfitCenterText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(textTable.PRCTR)=0 then textTable.PRCTR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM textTable.PRCTR )END) AS PRCTR,textTable.KOKRS,languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU,textTable.KTEXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cepct" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.PRCTR IS NOT NULL and textTable.KOKRS IS NOT NULL and textTable.DATBI = (SELECT MAX(DATBI) FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cepct" AS CEPCT1 WHERE CEPCT1.MANDT = ''800'' AND CEPCT1.PRCTR = textTable.PRCTR AND CEPCT1.KOKRS = textTable.KOKRS AND CEPCT1.SPRAS = textTable.SPRAS) AND textTable.DATBI >= TO_DATS(CURRENT_DATE) and textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_BusinessAreaText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.GSBER, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.GTEXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tgsbt" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.GSBER IS NOT NULL and textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialTypeText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.MTART , languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.MTBEZ FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t134t" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._VALID_FROM <= current_timestamp and languageTable._VALID_TO is null WHERE textTable.MTART IS NOT NULL and textTable.mandt = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialGroupText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.MATKL, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.WGBEZ FROM  "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_t023t" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._VALID_FROM <= current_timestamp and languageTable._VALID_TO is null WHERE textTable.MATKL IS NOT NULL and textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_MaterialText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(textTable.MATNR)=0 then textTable.MATNR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM textTable.MATNR )END) AS MATNR, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.maktx FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_makt" AS textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_mara" AS mara ON textTable.mandt= mara.mandt AND textTable.MATNR = mara.MATNR AND ifnull(mara.LVORM,'''')<>''X'' INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null LEFT OUTER JOIN "sap.plc.db::map.t_uom_mapping" AS uom ON mara.MEINS = uom.SOURCE_UOM_ID WHERE IFNULL(textTable.MATNR, '''') <> '''' AND (IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID,MEINS) IN (SELECT DISTINCT UOM_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_uom")) and textTable.mandt = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_DocumentTypeText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.DOKAR, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.DARTXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tdwat" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.CVLANG = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.DOKAR IS NOT NULL and textTable.mandt = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_DocumentStatusText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.DOKST, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.DOSTX FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tdwst" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.CVLANG = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.DOKST IS NOT NULL AND textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_DocumentText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT textTable.DOKAR, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(textTable.DOKNR)=0 then textTable.DOKNR else TRIM( LEADING ''0'' FROM textTable.DOKNR )END) AS DOKNR, textTable.DOKVR, textTable.DOKTL, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.DKTXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_drat" as textTable INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_draw" as draw ON textTable.DOKAR = draw.DOKAR AND textTable.DOKNR = draw.DOKNR AND textTable.DOKVR = draw.DOKVR AND textTable.DOKTL = draw.DOKTL AND ifnull(draw.LOEDK,'''')<>''X'' AND draw.mandt = ''800'' INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.LANGU= languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE textTable.DOKAR IS NOT NULL AND textTable.DOKNR IS NOT NULL AND textTable.DOKVR IS NOT NULL AND textTable.DOKTL IS NOT NULL AND textTable.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_ActivityPrice
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: select distinct ''ERP_STANDARD_PRICE'' as PRICE_SOURCE_ID, cssl.KOKRS as CONTROLLING_AREA_ID, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(cssl.KOSTL)=0 then cssl.KOSTL else TRIM(LEADING ''0'' from cssl.KOSTL) END) as COST_CENTER_ID, cssl.LSTAR as ACTIVITY_TYPE_ID, ''*'' as PROJECT_ID, ''*'' as CUSTOMER_ID, to_date(concat(cost.GJAHR,MM)) as VALID_FROM , add_days(add_months(to_date(concat(cost.GJAHR,MM)),1), -1) as VALID_TO , 1 as VALID_FROM_QUANTITY, null as VALID_TO_QUANTITY, case MM when ''01'' then cost.TOF001 when ''02'' then cost.TOF002 when ''03'' then cost.TOF003 when ''04'' then cost.TOF004 when ''05'' then cost.TOF005 when ''06'' then cost.TOF006 when ''07'' then cost.TOF007 when ''08'' then cost.TOF008 when ''09'' then cost.TOF009 when ''10'' then cost.TOF010 when ''11'' then cost.TOF011 when ''12'' then cost.TOF012 else null end as PRICE_FIXED_PORTION           , case MM when ''01'' then cost.TOG001 - cost.TOF001 when ''02'' then cost.TOG002 - cost.TOF002 when ''03'' then cost.TOG003 - cost.TOF003 when ''04'' then cost.TOG004 - cost.TOF004 when ''05'' then cost.TOG005 - cost.TOF005 when ''06'' then cost.TOG006 - cost.TOF006 when ''07'' then cost.TOG007 - cost.TOF007 when ''08'' then cost.TOG008 - cost.TOF008 when ''09'' then cost.TOG009 - cost.TOF009 when ''10'' then cost.TOG010 - cost.TOF010 when ''11'' then cost.TOG011 - cost.TOF011 when ''12'' then cost.TOG012 - cost.TOF012 else null end as PRICE_VARIABLE_PORTION, csks.WAERS as TRANSACTION_CURRENCY_ID , cost.TOE001 as PRICE_UNIT, IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID, csla.LEINH) as PRICE_UNIT_UOM_ID from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cost" as cost inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_cssl" as cssl on  cssl.MANDT = cost.MANDT and cssl.OBJNR = cost.OBJNR and cssl.GJAHR = cost.GJAHR inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_csks" as csks on  csks.MANDT = cssl.MANDT and csks.KOSTL = cssl.KOSTL and csks.KOKRS = cssl.KOKRS inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_csla" as csla on  csla.MANDT = cssl.MANDT and csla.KOKRS = cssl.KOKRS and csla.LSTAR = cssl.LSTAR inner join ( select ''01'' as MM from dummy union select ''02'' as MM from dummy union select ''03'' as MM from dummy union select ''04'' as MM from dummy union select ''05'' as MM from dummy union select ''06'' as MM from dummy union select ''07'' as MM from dummy union select ''08'' as MM from dummy union select ''09'' as MM from dummy union select ''10'' as MM from dummy union select ''11'' as MM from dummy union select ''12'' as MM from dummy ) on  1 = 1 left outer join "sap.plc.db::map.t_uom_mapping" AS uom ON uom.SOURCE_UOM_ID = csla.LEINH where add_days(add_months(to_date(concat(cost.GJAHR,MM)),1), -1) > TO_DATE(''20201231'') and (IFNULL(uom.DESTINATION_UOM_ID, csla.LEINH) IN (SELECT DISTINCT UOM_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_uom")) and (csks.WAERS is NULL or ucase(csks.WAERS) in ( SELECT distinct CURRENCY_ID FROM "sap.plc.db::basis.t_currency" where _valid_from <= current_timestamp and _valid_to is null) ) and cost.MANDT = ''800''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_WorkCenter
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: select distinct workCenter.ARBPL, workCenter.WERKS, CASE workCenter.VERWE when ''0001'' THEN ''MACHINE'' when ''0002'' THEN ''MACHINE_GROUP'' when ''0003'' THEN ''LABOR'' when ''0004'' THEN ''LABOR_GROUP'' when ''0005'' THEN ''PLANT_MAINTENANCE'' when ''0007'' THEN ''WORK_CENTER_ON_PRODUCTION_LINE'' when ''0008'' THEN ''PROCESSING_UNIT'' when ''0010'' THEN ''TRANSPORTATION_UNIT'' when ''0011'' THEN ''PRODUCTION_LINE'' when ''0012'' THEN ''ZONE'' when ''0013'' THEN ''STATION'' when ''Z001'' THEN ''DESIGN_AND_DEVELOPMENT'' when ''Z002'' THEN ''EXTERNAL_PROCESSING_UNIT'' when ''Z003'' THEN ''STORAGE_UNIT'' ELSE '''' END AS VERWE, (CASE WHEN "sap.plc.db.masterdata_replication.functions::f_is_numeric"(workCenterCost.KOSTL)=0 then workCenterCost.KOSTL else TRIM(LEADING ''0'' from workCenterCost.KOSTL )END) as KOSTL, workCenterCost.KOKRS, workCenter.VERAN, efficiencyRate.ZGKAL from "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_crhd" as workCenter inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_crco" as workCenterCost on workCenter.MANDT = workCenterCost.MANDT and workCenter.OBJTY = workCenterCost.OBJTY and workCenter.OBJID = workCenterCost.OBJID and workCenterCost.begda <= to_date(current_timestamp) and workCenterCost.endda > to_date(current_timestamp) left outer join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_tc31a" as efficiencyRate on  workCenter.MANDT = efficiencyRate.MANDT and workCenter.ZGR01 = efficiencyRate.ZGRAD and efficiencyRate.datub > to_date(current_timestamp) where workCenter.MANDT = ''800'' and workCenter.begda <= to_date(current_timestamp) and workCenter.endda > to_date(current_timestamp) and workCenter.ARBPL IS NOT NULL AND workCenter.WERKS IS NOT NULL and ifnull(workCenter.LVORM,'''')<>''X''

LABEL: XFLD_DisplayName_WorkCenterText
INPUT_SQL_DEFAULT: SELECT distinct workCenter.ARBPL, workCenter.WERKS, languageTable.LANGUAGE AS LANGU, textTable.KTEXT FROM "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_crtx" AS textTable inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_crhd" as workCenter on textTable.MANDT = workCenter.MANDT and textTable.OBJTY = workCenter.OBJTY and textTable.OBJID = workCenter.OBJID and workCenter.begda <= to_date(current_timestamp) and workCenter.endda > to_date(current_timestamp) and ifnull(workCenter.LVORM,'''')<>''X'' inner join "sap.plc.db::repl_st.t_crco" as workCenterCost on workCenter.MANDT = workCenterCost.MANDT and workCenter.OBJTY = workCenterCost.OBJTY and workCenter.OBJID = workCenterCost.OBJID and workCenterCost.begda <= to_date(current_timestamp) and workCenterCost.endda > to_date(current_timestamp) INNER JOIN "sap.plc.db::basis.t_language" as languageTable on textTable.SPRAS = languageTable.MAPPING_LANGUAGE_ID and languageTable.TEXTS_MAINTAINABLE = 1 and languageTable._valid_from <= current_timestamp and languageTable._valid_to is null WHERE workCenter.ARBPL IS NOT NULL AND workCenter.WERKS IS NOT NULL AND textTable.MANDT = ''800''
